# Prunr {{VERSION}}

Notarized alpha build. **Install manually once** — future updates via the in-app updater (Check for Updates… in the menu bar menu or Settings).

## Install

1. Download `Prunr-{{VERSION}}-build{{BUILD}}-macos.zip`
2. Unzip and drag **Prunr.app** to Applications
3. Open Prunr

Requires macOS 14+.
